doctype html
html
  head
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width')
    meta(http-equiv='Content-Type', content='text/html; charset=UTF-8')
    title Anomaly Alert - Request Limit Exceeded
  body(style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6;")
    div(style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);")
      div(style="background: #d32f2f; color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;")
        h1(style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px;") ⚠️ Request Limit Exceeded Alert
      
      div(style="padding: 20px;")
        p Hi #{firstName},
        
        p(style="font-weight: bold; color: #d32f2f;") 
          | An institute has exceeded the request limit and is attempting to create more requests.
        
        div(style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;")
          h2(style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #333;") Institute Details:
          ul(style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;")
            li 
              strong Name: 
              span #{instituteName}
            li 
              strong Contact Person: 
              span #{institutePerson}
            li 
              strong Email: 
              span #{instituteEmail}
            li 
              strong Attempt Time: 
              span #{attemptTime}
        
        div(style="background: #fff3e0; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; margin: 20px 0;")
          p(style="margin: 0;")
            | The institute has made 
            strong #{requestCount} requests 
            | in the last #{daysCount} days.
            br
            | Recommended limit: 
            strong #{warningThreshold} requests

        p(style="color: #d32f2f;") 
          strong Action Required: 
          | Please review this institute's activity.
        
        div(style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;")
          a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank', style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #1976d2; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;") View All Requests

        hr(style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 20px 0;")
        
        p(style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;") 
          | This is an automated alert. Please take appropriate action if needed.
        p(style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;") - System Alert 